                          Release 1.0
                                   

   CoolIO is a little commodity that allows various client-tasks that
   do not support the datatypes.library to load any image format, or
   to save under any file format.


      I. @{"Overview          " link "Overview" 0} ...believe me, its a quick one !
     II. @{"Installation      " link "Installation" 0} ...yes, but how to remove it now ?
    III. @{"Requirements      " link "Requirements" 0} ...you need at least a Pentium 133
     IV. @{"Configuration     " link "Configuration" 0} ...and you will know what the word "FUN"
